name: Prologue
description:
This workout takes you through a prologue. These are short, time trial stages that are usually at the start of a stage race. They present another opportunity for the sprinters to take victory as the short and had nature of the race suits the capacities of the sprinters. By simulating a prologue effort we will work on your high-end powers and get you to put your training of previous weeks to the test!
